- compiler executes the code from top to bottom

1. Decision Making Statement
	a) if statement
	b) switch statement

2. Loop Statement
	a) for loop
	b) while loop
	c) do while loop
	d) for each loop

3. Jump Statement
	a) break
	b) continue


